  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Your senses take on a keen draconic edge. You gain either darkvision with a range of 60 feet or low-light vision.</p>\n<p>At 5th level, you can select darkvision with a range of 60 feet or low-light vision if you do not yet have both, or you can add 60 feet to the range of your darkvision.</p>\n<p>At 11th level, you gain blindsense with a range of 30 feet. If you already have blindsense, you instead increase its range by 30 feet.</p>\n<p>At 15th level, you gain either the scent ability or a +4 bonus on Perception checks.</p>",
